# Repository layout (Testbee)

**Agents:** Also read `.cursor/memory.md` at task start (stack, branch, Decisions Log).

## Project root — Next.js / tooling only

Keep at repo root: `app/`, `components/`, `lib/`, `hooks/`, `store/`, `types/`, `public/`, `supabase/`, `modal-rag/`, `scripts/`, `data/`, `docs/`, plus config (`next.config.ts`, `middleware.ts`, `tsconfig.json`, `package.json`, `vitest.config.ts`, `.cursorrules`, `README.md`).

**Do not add** to root: markdown notes, `.log`, `.json` debug dumps, `.sqlite`, `__pycache__`, duplicate agent rule folders, or one-off scripts.

## Where things go

| Kind | Location |
|------|----------|
| App routes & API | `app/` |
| React UI | `components/` |
| Shared TS logic | `lib/` |
| React hooks | `hooks/` |
| Zustand | `store/` |
| SQL migrations | `supabase/migrations/` |
| Python RAG (Modal) | `modal-rag/` |
| Runnable TS/Python tools | `scripts/` (legacy/orphans → `scripts/legacy/`) |
| Product & architecture docs | `docs/` (`docs/gyan/`, `docs/branches/`, `docs/architecture/`, `docs/cursor/`) |
| Transient logs & API dumps | `docs/dev-notes/` (gitignored where noted) |
| Local SQLite / caches | `data/local-cache/` (gitignored) |
| Cursor agent memory & SQL notes | `.cursor/memory.md`, `.cursor/docs/` |
| Cursor rules (`.mdc`) | `.cursor/rules/` only — **not** `.cursor/.cursor/rules/` |
| CodeGraph index | `.codegraph/` (local index, gitignored) |

## Cursor rules in this repo

- `.cursorrules` — entrypoint; always read
- `.cursor/rules/codegraph.mdc` — CodeGraph MCP
- `.cursor/rules/karpathy-guidelines.mdc` — coding behavior
- `.cursor/rules/repo-layout.mdc` — this file

Human setup notes: `docs/cursor/karpathy-guidelines-setup.md`

## Before deleting or moving files

1. Confirm nothing imports the path (use CodeGraph or search).
2. Prefer **move** over delete for docs and scripts.
3. Never commit `.env`, `__pycache__/`, `data/local-cache/`, or `.next/`.
